data.description: On Canal.  This 2 bedroom split plan, 2 bath Bungalow/Ranch dwelling only a block from the lake has been tastefully painted and landscaped.  Entire roof has been replaced with metal and extra R (39) factor to enhance efficient wall unit AC,s.  Vinyl flooring throughout makes upkeep easy.  Barn doors add to the design, along with extra special lighting under kitchen cabinets and in living room ceiling.  Property has public water and well and updated plumbing.  Septic drainfield is new.  Dining room has large windows and a built in pantry.  Bedrooms with walk-in closets are large enough for whatever size your furniture may be.  Carport will protect your vehicles and leads you to a restful patio for morning coffee or after dinner relaxing.
